          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Lanceur d'alerte</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Signalement confidentiel</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Amelioration de la transparence, integrite et gouvernance interne</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-l-secondary hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Investigations RH internes</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Independantes</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Objectivise les faits dans les situations sensibles</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Securise la decision par une demarche impartiale</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-l-secondary hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Mediation sociale</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Resolution des conflits</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Desamorce les tensions avant escalade</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Reduction des couts de conflit</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Protection du climat social</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {/* <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-l-secondary hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Verification cotisations IPRES</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Sous-traitants et interimaires</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Reduit l'exposition aux risques de non-conformite lies aux prestataires</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Verifie la realite des cotisations</li>
          </ul>
        </div> */}

