          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Permis de travail expatries</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Conseil et gestion</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Securise le statut des expatries</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Limite les ruptures d'activite liees aux retards administratifs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-l-secondary hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Audit facturation interimaires</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2 font-medium">Controle et verification</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Detecte anomalies et surcouts</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Maitrise de la depense et fiabilisation de la relation prestataire</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 border-l-4 border-l-secondary hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900">Gestion proactive des risques RH et juridiques</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1.5 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Anticipe les non-conformites et litiges</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Diagnostic, priorisation et plan d'actions</li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-secondary mr-2 mt-0.5">&#8226;</span>Reduction du risque juridique</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </SectionContainer>

    <!-- Section Tarification -->
    <SectionContainer>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-secondary/5 rounded-2xl p-12 border border-primary/10">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Tarification : sur demande</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
            La tarification depend des outils et services souscrits. Contactez-nous pour obtenir un devis adapte a votre entreprise.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
